{
  "stem": "5275.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because they have found that Anka is not living, I have told them my real name.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They know the address of my relative, Stephen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Krisia, go to him this Saturday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Perhaps you will still make it in time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He should go find work on the estate of the count, or in your place, anywhere, even the Baudinst.' Baudinst was a German work place that they got people to work on German programs.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And with my false papers, I guess, and without them looking any deeper into it, they probably would have kept me there and I would work there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 'Perhaps he will succeed to cover his steps and then go to Chernigov.' That's another city there. 'I do not need anything, only peace of mind [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] that he's free.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] I will not burden you with anything else, only this one time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you will not be able to go Saturday, you must go on a weekday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Give Stephen my postcard to read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He will be brave and won't be preoccupied with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Give 200 zlotys to the man who will give you this letter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Keep in touch with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I want to know what will happen to Stephen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Go to our office quickly, take our photo-- no, take out photo from my desk and give it to Stephen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There are two pieces-- there are three pieces of soap in the desk drawer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Sell them for 120 zloty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] You will have enough for this man for two times.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ask him if he has sent Stephen 120 zloty I gave him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If not, ask for it firmly and give them to Stephen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I also have sent Stephen 400 zloty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did he receive it?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
